org.trippi.io

Class SimpleTripleParsingContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.trippi.io.SimpleParsingContext<org.jrdf.graph.Triple>
      • org.trippi.io.SimpleTripleParsingContext
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.openrdf.rio.RDFHandler

    public class SimpleTripleParsingContext
extends SimpleParsingContext<org.jrdf.graph.Triple>
    An iterator over triples parsed by a RIO rdf parser. Unlike the SimpleParser, this implementation will return an iterator capable of serializing its triples to a stream with source-defined prefixes
    Author:
